== Politiki yo kwegereza ubuyobozi abaturage ==
Iyi politiki kandi ifite ishingiro mu mategeko shingiro y’igihugu ndetse no mu ivugurura rya politiki n’ubuyobozi guverinoma imaze gushyira mu bikorwa.Mu myaka yashize u Rwanda rwashoboye kugera ku ntera nziza yo kuzamuka mu bukungu. Guverinoma ishyira ingufu mu gushyigikira ibyiciro byinshi by'abaturage bibasirwa n'ubukene barimo abantu bakuze, ababana n'ubumuga, abana bato, ingo ziyobowe n'abagore, abarokotse Jenoside yakorewe Abatutsi ndetse n'abasizwe inyuma mu mateka. Urubyiruko ni itsinda naryo rikeneye inkunga, urebye ingorane benshi bafite mukubona akazi kubera ubumenyi buke.<ref>www.minaloc.gov.rw</ref>
